original_title: The Incredibly Strange, Sad Story Behind The World's Most Ambitious Demo Tape
overview: In the latest episode of OUTSIDER, VICE tracks down aspiring filmmaker/actor Laz Rojas to uncover the mystery behind his insanely ambitious '90s audition tape that features his performance of over 100 male/female characters.
title: The Incredibly Strange, Sad Story Behind The World's Most Ambitious Demo Tape
